title: DDFP 435: QBs of Super Bowl LX & Shek's Mustache
itunes:title: DDFP 435: QBs of Super Bowl LX & Shek's Mustache
description:
Shek sits down with Handsome Hank for the first Audio Only podcast of the season. They talk about the latest news regarding both T.O. and Marvin Harrison as well as Peyton Manning's future. The guys then review fan tweets/rankings as well as release Shek's QBs of Super Bowl LX rankings. Will Peyton Manning make the list? Will the guys agree on a top QB? Did Shek really shave? Find out more on DDFP.
